description.en: Jack Raffle is a meme token but with actual unique utility that incentivizes its holders by letting them earn $BNB. All $JACKR holders are able to claim BNB rewards daily from a pool that is generated from transactions. On top of that, you are automatically part of a daily, weekly and monthly raffle! Get your chunk of Jack's $BNB Pot just by holding $JACKR! Secure, Fun & Easy – on Binance Smart Chain.
